    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. It has been well-maintained and shows only minor signs of wear on the interior and exterior. All mechanical systems are functioning properly, and the car is reliable for daily use.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a great choice for someone looking for a dependable car without the premium price tag of a newer model. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are solid and have been well-maintained, ensuring it starts and runs reliably for your daily commute. However, potential buyers should be aware of several cosmetic issues, including some noticeable scratches on the passenger side doors and fading paint on the hood. The interior shows signs of regular use with some wear on the driver's seat upholstery and a few minor stains on the carpet. While it isn't a showpiece, it is a functional and honest vehicle that gets the job done.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for the discerning driver. This unit exhibits a refined balance of performance and reliability, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation. It remains in commendable condition, offering a sophisticated driving experience and serving as a testament to its previous stewardship. This is an ideal acquisition for those seeking a high-caliber vehicle that bridges the gap between value and distinction.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is stylish? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s been a total joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or those fun weekend road trips. It runs smoothly and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Available now is this mid-engine 2014 Porsche Cayman, a masterclass in chassis balance and mechanical engagement. Power is delivered by a 2.7L naturally aspirated flat-six, mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox that offers short, mechanical throws and perfect gear spacing. The vehicle features a rigid monocoque construction and a finely tuned MacPherson strut suspension setup, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback through the rack. This example has been properly maintained, with recent service including a full ignition coil refresh and a high-flow air filter installation to optimize the induction note. The braking system remains sharp with significant life remaining on the ventilated rotors and multi-piston calipers. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with a well-loved driver's car, its structural integrity and drivetrain performance remain robust for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Interior and exterior are solid.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and care, presenting in very clean condition throughout. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though I want to note a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, two-inch light scratch near the rear wheel well that is only visible upon close inspection. The alloy wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin smells fresh and has never been smoked in. The leather seating surfaces are firm and intact, with only the expected light softening of the leather on the driver's outer bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions perfectly, including the ice-cold dual-zone climate control and the premium audio system. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change, new air filters, and a multi-point inspection completed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and seamless. This is an honest, well-maintained example perfect for a discerning driver.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies reliability and performance. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Offering a balanced combination of luxury and utility, this vehicle remains in commendable condition, ready for its next discerning owner. Experience the assurance of quality engineering and a well-documented service history.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next big adventure? This car has been well-loved and is in really solid shape. It runs super smoothly and still looks great on the road! I've kept up with it, so it's totally ready for you to hop in and drive away today. I\u2019m happy to answer any questions you have, so don't be shy\u2014let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the rev range. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the rod bearings have been proactively serviced. The suspension geometry remains precise, benefiting from refreshed control arm bushings and consistent damping. While the paint and interior show honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, providing the visceral, high-RPM engagement and balanced chassis dynamics this platform is renowned for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
